      • buildDoor

        public void buildDoor(int roomNumber1,
                      int roomNumber2,
                      Direction dir,
                      boolean open)
        Build a new door in the current Maze between two the specified rooms.
        指定者:
        buildDoor 在接口中 MazeBuilder
        参数:
        roomNumber1 - specifies the room number of the first room
        roomNumber2 - specifies the room number of the second room
        dir - specifies the side of the first room at which the door will be located the second room will be on the other side of the door.
        open - whether the door is open or not
